"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/592891","Home Office","false","2016-10-13","<p>The Government is not aware of any British citizens, including children, residing in the La Linière migrant camp.</p>",,"Baroness Williams of Trafford","HL2016 ; HL2018","2016-10-13T14:28:19.207Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/592891/answer","Biography information for Baroness Williams of Trafford","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/592891/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/592891/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2016-10-03","Migrant Camps: Dunkirk","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what steps, if any, they are taking to provide assistance to British citizens, particularly British children, in La Linière refugee camp outside Dunkirk.","false","Biography information for Baroness Hamwee",,"Baroness Hamwee","HL2017"
